NAME
    Acme::CPANModules::CryptoExchange::API - Modules that interface to
    cryptocurrency exchanges

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.003 of
    Acme::CPANModules::CryptoExchange::API (from Perl distribution
    Acme-CPANModules-CryptoExchange-API), released on 2018-09-22.

DESCRIPTION
    Modules that interface to cryptocurrency exchanges.

INCLUDED MODULES
    *   WebService::Cryptopia

    *   WebService::Binance

    *   Finance::Indodax

    *   Finance::BitFlip

    *   Finance::Bank::Kraken

    *   Poloniex::API

    *   WWW::API::Bitfinex

    *   Finance::BitStamp::API

    *   Finance::GDAX::API - Last time I tried, not working

        Alternate modules: Finance::GDAX::Lite

    *   Finance::GDAX::Lite - An alternative which I wrote because
        Finance::GDAX::API was not working

    *   Finance::LocalBitcoins::API

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Acme-CPANModules-CryptoExchange-API>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-Acme-CPANModules-CryptoExchange-API>.

